de-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">It&#8217;s like looking at the Premier League table in October. There&#8217;s a trickle of results that give you an idea of how the season might play out, but not nearly enough to say for sure. Will this be the season for underdogs like Villa and Brighton to make a big push for Top Four? Will the usual suspects from Manchester, Liverpool and London come out on top like they always do? Is this all an exercise in futility as we await City&#8217;s inevitable coronation? We&#8217;ll only know come the summer. [Source: <a href="https://theanalyst.com/eu/2023/10/premier-league-2023-24-title-and-top-four-predictions-october-update/">Opta Analyst</a>]</figcaption></figure></div><p>With that being said, I&#8217;ve been able to have close to a hundred conversations with participants from every corner of the ONDC ecosystem over the past four months (including several of the major protagonists). The anecdotal evidence from these conversations coupled with public data and news reports make for a decent sketch of the present ONDC chessboard.</p><h2>So what <em>does</em> the chessboard look like?</h2><p>It&#8217;s buzzing. There&#8217;s a pretty diverse caste of participants that are either already live or in queue to join the network. This includes new startups, old startups, established enterprises, logistics companies, financial services companies, tech providers, and everything in between.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F792e9ab3-766d-4518-bb89-981aea13b198_1437x730.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F792e9ab3-766d-4518-bb89-981aea13b198_1437x730.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F792e9ab3-766d-4518-bb89-981aea13b198_1437x730.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F792e9ab3-766d-4518-bb89-981aea13b198_1437x730.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F792e9ab3-766d-4518-bb89-981aea13b198_1437x730.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_2400,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F792e9ab3-766d-4518-bb89-981aea13b198_1437x730.png" width="1200" height="609.6033402922756" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/792e9ab3-766d-4518-bb89-981aea13b198_1437x730.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:false,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;large&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:730,&quot;width&quot;:1437,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;bytes&quot;:337031,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-large" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F792e9ab3-76