 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F342adbc3-38ee-4e73-9db2-394aa02d7ccd_939x527.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/maggax_ondc-2024-with-recap-of-2023-activity-7149273392808927232-T2KI/?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=member_desktop">Plotch.ai</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>2. The <strong>number of sellers</strong> on the network grew from <a href="https://government.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/technology/ondc-set-for-a-bumper-2023-with-85-cities-800-merchants-and-26-participants-already-on-board-mdceo-t-koshy/96659864">800 in Jan &#8216;23</a> to just under 90,000 by the end of the year. This includes brands and merchants that have set up their own shop directly on the network or are onboarding via third party seller apps. There were 26 <em>live</em> <strong>network participants</strong> at the start of last year (including buyer apps, seller apps and logistics providers). That number stands at 65 today, with over <a href="https://ondc.org/network-participants/">15,000 participants</a> at various stages of integration.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_2400,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png" width="1200" height="382.7586206896552" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/be687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:false,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;large&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:370,&quot;width&quot;:1160,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;bytes&quot;:91072,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-large" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe687595-0d00-4338-965c-bb59cd2eaf0b_1160x370.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4LNHZo-k6iU&amp;t=1526s">ONDC</a></figcaption></figure></div><h2>What are people buying?</h2><p>Out of the <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/tech/technology/ondc-crosses-record-5-5-million-transactions-in-december/articleshow/106552745.cms?from=mdr">5.5 million transactions</a> in December last year:</p><ul><li><p>63% (~3.4 million) were in the mobility category</p></li><li><p>37% (~2 million) were in retail</p></li></ul><p>Within the retail category:</p><ul><li><p>32.5% were in food and beverages</p></li><li><p>29.6% were in fashion</p></li><li><p>12.6% were home and kitchen purchases</p></li><li><p>10.1% were grocery transactions</p></li><li><p>8.5% were for beauty and personal care products</p></li><li><p>5.7% were electronics purchases</p></li></ul><h2>Can you go a little deeper?</h2><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif" width="530" height="334.17670682730926" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:314,&quot;width&quot;:498,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:530,&quot;bytes&quot;:4026196,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/gif&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bc91dd0-bfaf-4fab-91d6-12604ace7cb1_498x314.gif 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">I assume most of you stopped reading a while ago anyway</figcaption></figure></div><p>Sorry. </p><p>And yes, sure.</p><p>When reflecting on the adoption of ONDC in 2023, it&#8217;s useful to divide the quantum of transactions into Mobility and non-Mobility (AKA Retail) use cases.</p><h2>Let&#8217;s start with mobility?</h2><p><a href="https://resources.ondc.org/mobility">Mobility</a> means anything that makes it easier for people to move around. It theoretically includes everything from ride hailing to bike sharing to public transport and travel services. It&#8217;s been one of the bright spots of the ONDC era.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png" width="895" height="798" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:798,&quot;width&quot;:895,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:387241,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe36260c8-baf6-45af-8d6b-d660e51855cb_895x798.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>New ONDC-based ride-hailing apps have sprung up all around the country in different constructs over the past 12 months (led by transport unions, new startups, groups of drivers etc). They&#8217;ve become a genuine threat to the duopoly of Uber and Ola. These ventures are encouched in the same thesis - that the current omnipotent platform model isn&#8217;t working for either drivers or riders anymore. </p><p>The lack of transparency over fees, caprice of surge pricing, frequent cancellation of rides, and lack of a voice in governance means that both drivers and riders are unsatisfied with the current set up of leading mobility platforms.</p><p>The protocol approach liberates drivers from having to pay 15-25% of their earnings to Uber/Ola. Instead, ONDC-based apps like Namma Yatri have chosen to work on a fixed subscription model where drivers pay ~Rs. 25 as a flat daily fee or Rs. 3.5 per trip (up to a maximum of Rs. 25 per day). This means that drivers take home 100% of the commission they make from each ride directly from their customers. So far this has led to a greater satisfaction from drivers that previously lamented their subservience to Uber/Ola. This, in turn, has created a more reliable supply of drivers in places like Bangalore and Kolkata, leading to more satisfied customers. The 12-month results of Namma Yatri speak for itself.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png" width="1080" height="414" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:414,&quot;width&quot;:1080,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:57649,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ccdb9fa-7b71-428a-91b8-8b0b0fe5278e_1080x414.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">via the Namma Yatri <a href="https://nammayatri.in/open/">open data portal</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>In many ways Mobility was ground zero for ONDC, considering that Beckn was first tested and proven as a concept with the <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/tech/technology/more-than-7-6k-rides-availed-by-commuters-on-kochi-open-mobility-network/articleshow/96388344.cms?from=mdr">Kochi Open Mobility Network (KOMN)</a> in July 2021. Back then the KOMN <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/tech/technology/more-than-7-6k-rides-availed-by-commuters-on-kochi-open-mobility-network/articleshow/96388344.cms?from=mdr">helped to onboard</a> various transport services and unions into a single portal to test the efficacy of this model. Fast forward three and a half year and the results of various open mobility initiatives present arguably the strongest case that ONDC won&#8217;t just be a flash in the pan.</p><h2>What about retail?</h2><p>ONDC has steadily expanded the scope of its retail syllabus over the course of 2023. The original pilot was aimed at two major areas - Food &amp; Beverages, and Groceries, largely because:</p><ul><li><p>For F&amp;B: on the buyer side, we have become exceedingly comfortable with the rigmarole of ordering food online. On the seller side, Indian restaurant owners are perpetually at odds with major food delivery platforms (like Zomato and Swiggy) because of their predilection for deep discounting and high commission rates (25-40%), and unilateral control over customer data.</p></li><li><p>For Groceries: on the buyer side, groceries (food, snacks, FMCG items, personal care products, fruits and vegetables etc) are a frequent daily purchase category accounting for <a href="https://www.investindia.gov.in/sector/retail-e-commerce/food-retail">65%</a> of retail consumption in India and <a href="https://www.livemint.com/industry/retail/less-affluent-households-spend-2-000-on-monthly-groceries-11667242654408.html">25-50%</a> of monthly household spends. On the seller side, despite groceries contributing to over <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/1222343/india-grocery-spend-as-a-share-of-gdp/">20%</a> of India&#8217;s GDP, it has only <a href="https://ondc-static-website-media.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/res/daea2fs3n/image/upload/ondc-website/files/democratising-digital-commerce-in-india-april-2023.pdf">1-2%</a> of the overall share of India&#8217;s digital commerce market.</p></li></ul><p>As more specialised seller apps have entered the fray (to onboard specific types and categories of sellers), the diversity of product categories on ONDC has expanded into things like fashion, electronics, home appliances, beauty and personal care etc. By October of last year there were more than <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=how+many+SKUs+on+ONDC&amp;rlz=1C5CHFA_enIN926IN926&amp;oq=how+many+SKUs+on+ONDC&amp;aqs=chrome..69i57j0i512j0i22i30l4j0i390i512i650l3.3114j0j7&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8#ip=1:~:text=ONDC%20Preps%20To,walk%2Dfintech%2Dro...">75 lakh SKUs</a> available for sale on ONDC.</p><blockquote><p><em>&#8220;&#8230;in few years time, every product or service which is relevant to a broad cross-section of users will make their product catalog visible in the open network using this open protocol, and diverse kinds of buying applications will come and help their relevant kinds of buyers to access the products relevant [to them].&#8221;</em><br><strong>- <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EEC8qdRfhRQ&amp;ab_channel=moneycontrol">T. Koshy</a> (CEO - ONDC)</strong></p></blockquote><h2>Is there anything you can&#8217;t buy on ONDC?</h2><p>Love, respect, and admiration. </p><p>Just kidding (ish). </p><p>Jokes aside, while almost all the action in Year 1 (and a half) has centred around Retail and Mobility, ONDC hopes to stretch its limbs towards more exotic territory in the months and years to come. In theory, in a fantastical 100% successful scenario, there should be nothing you <em>can&#8217;t</em> buy on ONDC.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_2400,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png" width="1200" height="741.0714285714286" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/efe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:false,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;large&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:830,&quot;width&quot;:1344,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;bytes&quot;:532326,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-large" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fefe9d527-fe52-419d-9ee8-85d40e4007f7_1344x830.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: McKinsey - &#8216;Democratising digital commerce in India&#8217;</figcaption></figure></div><p>To illustrate:</p><ul><li><p>- <strong><a href="https://resources.ondc.org/financial-services">Financial Services</a> is going to be a big part of the <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/17tlJYfy3_URwFxpKGDyCUqoM7EXktLPx/edit#slide=id.p10">ONDC roadmap</a>.</strong> A large part of India still remains woefully under-penetrated when it comes to products like lending and insurance. ONDC is <a href="https://www.moneycontrol.com/news/technology/ondc-pilots-finserv-foray-with-personal-loans-attracts-big-players-for-credit-insurance-mf-offerings-12150461.html">already building</a> the standardised API pipes to allow any (compliant) buyer app to offer financial services products to their users. Eg: By coming on board ONDC, MakeMyTrip could provide its users with a complete menu of travel insurance products from insurers that have integrated with the network. <br>- The ability to reach users via the applications that are part of their digital routines helps financial institutions (FIs) reduce their cost of customer acquisition and increase their footprint digitally, making smaller ticket FS products more viable. The addition of &#8216;embedded&#8217; credit and insurance products into the ONDC retail transaction flows also acts as an additional lubricant for purchase activity.</p></li></ul><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_2400,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png" width="886" height="485.1904761904762" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:false,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;large&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:736,&quot;width&quot;:1344,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:886,&quot;bytes&quot;:244402,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-large" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F539ecdb5-68f4-4afd-a1b0-c3e3a64b8678_1344x736.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/17tlJYfy3_URwFxpKGDyCUqoM7EXktLPx/edit#slide=id.p10">ONDC</a></figcaption></figure></div><ul><li><p><strong>- B2B on ONDC could arguably be an even bigger market opportunity than B2C.</strong> For all the ink that&#8217;s been spilled over the paucity of digitisation in our retail commerce flows, it dwarfs the quantum of business-to-business activity that is still done over paper and phone in India.<br>- To put this thesis to the test, last year two e-commerce enablement companies - Rapidor and SignCatch - played the role of buyer app and seller app to facilitate the <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/tech/technology/ondc-retail-tech-firm-signcatch-executes-first-b2b-transaction/articleshow/100426637.cms?from=mdr">first ever B2B transaction on ONDC</a>. They helped Organic Diet and Herbal Products (a Delhi-based company), to successfully receive an order from Swabharat Stores (a retail outlet based in Thane). At scale, this could vastly widen the market and streamline the operations of Indian businesses in the years to come.</p></li></ul><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F781e9ef6-3b29-4aeb-90b3-b1520cc0f9ad_720x311.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F781e9ef6-3b29-4aeb-90b3-b1520cc0f9ad_720x311.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F781e9ef6-3b29-4aeb-90b3-b1520cc0f9ad_720x311.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F781e9ef6-3b29-4aeb-90b3-b1520cc0f9ad_720x311.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F781e9ef6-3b29-4aeb-90b3-b1520cc0f9ad_720x311.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F781e9ef6-3b29-4aeb-90b3-b1520cc0f9ad_720x311.png" width="720" height="311" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.