its probably worth putting on some goggles and preparing for the show&#127871;.</p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://tigerfeathers.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;button-wrapper&quot;}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary button-wrapper" href="https://tigerfeathers.substack.com/subscribe?"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p><div><hr></div><h4>SOURCES AND FURTHER READING</h4><ul><li><p><a href="https://www.buildonondc.com/">Build On ONDC</a> by Antler India</p></li><li><p><a href="https://ondc.org/blog/ondc-launches-the-ondc-guide-app-for-sellers-buyers-and-more/">ONDC Official Guide App</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://ondc-static-website-media.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/res/daea2fs3n/image/upload/ondc-website/files/ONDCStrategyPaper_ucvfjm/1659889490.pdf">The Way Ahead</a> by ONDC</p></li><li><p><a href="https://ondc-static-website-media.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/res/daea2fs3n/image/upload/ondc-website/files/ONDC_Building_Trust_Consultation_Vf_utbodw/1664541553.pdf">Building Trust in the ONDC Network</a> by ONDC</p></li><li><p><a href="https://ondc-static-website-media.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/res/daea2fs3n/image/upload/ondc-website/files/democratising-digital-commerce-in-india-april-2023.pdf">Democratising digital commerce in India</a> by McKinsey &amp; Co</p></li><li><p><a href="https://jmfl.com/Common/getFile/955">ONDC: Disruption or Evolution?</a> by JM Financial</p></li><li><p><a href="https://www.sattva.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/DP_ONDC-Primer_14042023.pdf">Open Network for Digital Commerce</a> by Sattva Knowledge Institute</p></li><li><p><a href="https://www.scribd.com/document/647862968/Jefferies-report-on-ONDC-being-the-new-challenger#">ONDC, a New Challenger in a Competitive Space?</a> by Jefferies</p></li><li><p><a href="https://www.performics.com/in/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2022/11/202